#
# BoJ Server: The Teranga Menu
#
# This menu is the public face of the Bundle of Joy server.
# AI agents act as the "Maitre D'" — presenting available capabilities
# to users as honoured guests (Teranga = hospitality in Wolof).
#
# The menu is organised into three tiers:
#   - Teranga: Core cartridges maintained by the project
#   - Shield: Privacy and security cartridges
#   - Ayo: Community-contributed cartridges (joy)

@canonical-location: `.machine_readable/servers/menu.a2ml`
@generated-from: `src/abi/Catalogue.idr` (IsUnbreakable proof required for Ready status)

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The 2D Capability Matrix
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#              MCP    LSP    DAP    BSP    NeSy   Agent  Fleet  gRPC   REST
#           ┌──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┬──────┐
# Cloud     │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Container │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Database  │  ●   │  ●   │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# K8s       │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Git       │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Secrets   │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Queues    │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# IaC       │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Observe   │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# SSG       │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Proof     │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │      │
# Fleet     │  ●   │      │      │      │      │      │  ●   │  ●   │      │
# NeSy      │  ●   │  ●   │      │      │  ●   │      │      │  ●   │      │
#           └──────┴──────┴──────┴──────┴──────┴──────┴──────┴──────┴──────┘
#
# ● = cartridge present (may be Development, Ready, or Faulty)
# Empty = no cartridge yet (future work)

