# Umoja Network (Community Nodes)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# The distributed hosting network. Nodes volunteer compute time.
# Hash attestation ensures integrity — tampered nodes are excluded
# from the community network but can still run locally.
#
# Like Tor or IPFS, but for developer server infrastructure.

